msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/bind-dirs.rst:172
#: 814ca24d207c44918f9d2af0120acc34
msgid ""
"To re-enable ``/home`` and ``/usr/local`` persistence, just add them to "
"the list:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/bind-dirs.rst:181
#: ca0b00ace107490e9d580f43b4958f05
msgid ""
"When starting the VM, declared custom-persist bind dirs are automatically"
" added to the ``binds`` variable described above and are handled in the "
